  %h3
    Participation rules

  %p
    In order to foster an environment conducive to civil and on-topic political discussion, please abide by the following rules. Violation of any of these rules may result in account suspension or deactivation.

  %ul
    %li
      Do not make personal attacks or use offensive language. Disagreement is both inevitable and welcome, but please refrain from name-calling; using expletives; slurs against race, ethnicity, gender, and sexual orientation; and other insults.
    %li
      Speak for yourself. The bottom line is, no one should be using this site as part of their paid advocacy duties.
    %li
      Though you may change your stance at any time, please sign up for and use one and only one account.


